<body>
    <h1>T4 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"742424242292" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"2db42785-0c73-4dd8-9018-4da014b1406a">
<h2 local-id=3D"f365fd6e81ef" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9ab908679e70">This document provides a comprehensive technic=
al overview of the DevOps implementation designed and deployed for hosting =
multiple frontend applications using AWS cloud services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a33d920bb31e">The purpose of this document is to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f299cae3-7e73-47f0-bdc0-d6091c5e852f">
<li local-id=3D"211a7f3b-5073-44d7-9f50-d5cb4f87d48f">
<p local-id=3D"6233d7b48e2a">Describe the architecture and infrastructure u=
sed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfce28df-dc40-41e7-87fb-9dbd85fde1fe">
<p local-id=3D"b3ddd695c630">Document deployment processes and tools</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"6462d980-6284-42fb-a792-9b101b92bfc4">
<p local-id=3D"0e698a9468b1">Explain security, scalability, and cost consid=
erations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"47af006b-1ce3-4082-a989-b9e9621b6b53">
<p local-id=3D"fcc7f047349e">Provide implementation transparency for stakeh=
olders</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"53451163fee4"><strong>Intended Audience:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b4f9fd22-f628-4a2f-b60e-2e7e527fdb38">
<li local-id=3D"12849b50-1add-4d97-bc64-a318707ac3da">
<p local-id=3D"4a107920e771">Chief Technology Officers (CTO)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff545ef4-41b2-41b5-8c45-70d55fa5b1d8">
<p local-id=3D"04aa310b2906">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ec50dec0-3f52-43a2-a4cd-ce5e9f0af507">
<p local-id=3D"bd709cebd1eb">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6174293d-af02-417a-9a8f-294bfba2e2a0">
<p local-id=3D"38d59933d5e4">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9a68a1b8-a92b-4741-9a50-30b427a334ab">
<p local-id=3D"a6e7e0abf083">Technical Resellers and Implementation Partner=
s</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"13a412863bd2">This document serves as a reference guide for =
understanding the system design, deployment workflow, operational model, an=
d architectural decisions.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"839e6e97-79ff-4bf0-b20d-bddbaa5e8150">
<h2 local-id=3D"ee56302c7c06" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"cd7af550ce3f">This document covers the implementation of a c=
loud-based DevOps solution that includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3f0591c9-d6ff-4b4d-92fa-e8713f17fe59">
<li local-id=3D"cdb8513a-0e5d-4e0d-a700-cd89092a1598">
<p local-id=3D"8a9d2d6a11dc">Static frontend hosting using Amazon S3</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"5678322f-942c-4456-89b9-8fca1f59242f">
<p local-id=3D"920aff9873c8">Containerized application deployment using Ama=
zon ECS (Fargate)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5da02501-3902-48f7-9841-caa9cc139ec9">
<p local-id=3D"a4611a4ca095">Docker image management via Amazon ECR</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"8e16beab-dbc3-4e9f-bff7-f723718677c4">
<p local-id=3D"4450ba46ff54">EC2-based frontend hosting using Nginx</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"dc408fba-809e-4b79-82df-c8737e2d7447">
<p local-id=3D"28fe9c27e208">Load balancing using Application Load Balancer=
 (ALB)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99d37671-e3d1-4847-8d77-ac8170518ae9">
<p local-id=3D"7d9b46ce6364">Basic security configuration using IAM and Sec=
urity Groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32ba5343-347c-434f-907f-b61e1a219277">
<p local-id=3D"a133382eff41">Infrastructure validation and deployment verif=
ication</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"27a6cb9bde00" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-InScope">In Scope<=
/h3>
<ul local-id=3D"18f3bb7a-6e0f-4698-9d88-256a0585dca4">
<li local-id=3D"f47cd7b7-7723-45da-a968-ab81da437fb1">
<p local-id=3D"760cf6aa4fdb">Infrastructure architecture design</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d75164b9-b20b-45ed-b044-35aa3e3b35fc">
<p local-id=3D"913cecf69c1a">Containerization workflow</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dad63e76-0c7a-431d-9a85-1c5a3305963e">
<p local-id=3D"51cf642027cc">Deployment strategy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8d4c606-bbd9-4fc8-83cb-79847640b9ce">
<p local-id=3D"1fef925aac0b">Environment configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9833b70b-97c8-4a0c-8b35-cb5aac368898">
<p local-id=3D"2f5d077b9892">Security group configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bed561c1-3eff-4cc6-869b-053bdcbb5ed8">
<p local-id=3D"c2389909b7e4">Application availability validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f709dc88-7438-4410-835d-08683c36face">
<p local-id=3D"c2a89eee55e1">Cost optimization considerations</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6c94d37d6380" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-OutofScope">Out of=
 Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ee71c384-63c6-4d21-9824-2d0484e8c908">
<li local-id=3D"3c554402-aeb6-445b-81e7-bd3d6777a0e0">
<p local-id=3D"d50983d7da2a">Backend API implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6128b5e0-e236-4949-8fd3-ce457b956d79">
<p local-id=3D"b3f1edab84a3">CI/CD automation using external pipelines (e.g=
., Jenkins, GitHub Actions)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7254378-b374-45a9-a67d-97866db71263">
<p local-id=3D"52e83f28c583">Domain configuration and SSL certificate manag=
ement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8244bd3-9614-486d-917c-8cf18a4fa13f">
<p local-id=3D"6042911cd219">Production-grade high availability across mult=
iple regions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"126404f3-0b90-4200-ae4b-58698da04b1c">
<p local-id=3D"ac5000b85e1e">Database deployment and configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"b15930ff324e" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"62a4d6a2-729c-42c9-b470-1a857dee5deb">
<h2 local-id=3D"1b4560ea2b49" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9faeae8bf3be">A DevOps Project integrates development and op=
erations practices to enable faster, reliable, and scalable software delive=
ry through automation, cloud infrastructure, and continuous deployment prin=
ciples.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d3ea39b3f70e">In this implementation, DevOps practices were =
applied to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"054932c7-c336-452b-bd15-92d3c6aafcdb">
<li local-id=3D"93299acf-6dbe-4c47-90c8-808984608384">
<p local-id=3D"dd6d1dd3d9af">Containerize frontend applications</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e1db30a-f9da-4fea-99aa-2e497cf98c4e">
<p local-id=3D"6a5ffc1baa41">Deploy them using AWS managed services</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"fe29e886-867b-40e8-a07b-13d11c65b30a">
<p local-id=3D"2c577e8f6c3a">Ensure scalability using load balancing</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"8840c004-0732-4e6d-b3e3-1daf57daa263">
<p local-id=3D"7c6172f834f1">Optimize infrastructure usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b89b2255-0114-4519-bb4f-470cd0606b04">
<p local-id=3D"1ced4794d7b7">Validate application availability in real time=
</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"143ac016d555" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-BenefitsAchieved">=
Benefits Achieved</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d968ee7c-eff0-492b-9e6a-ab012507e497">
<li local-id=3D"2627f6a2-7804-4817-94ee-2f7f3fc7f482">
<p local-id=3D"334f80873854">Faster deployment using containerized workload=
s</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11122f8d-7f1e-4d1c-839a-e85045591cf4">
<p local-id=3D"8aef8e1e90e1">Reduced manual configuration through managed A=
WS services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57553cfd-1b56-4051-aabc-1b139e7059d2">
<p local-id=3D"f44b9b6dd62b">Improved scalability using ECS Fargate and Loa=
d Balancer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6a5d5f8-ab49-4bb5-b88b-a2088f2c22ac">
<p local-id=3D"ef263b37970b">Better resource utilization via right-sized EC=
2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7de87686-56ca-4512-bf0f-11eda00a8d5a">
<p local-id=3D"64cace0e2aab">Simplified frontend hosting through S3 static =
website hosting</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ce3b3bef-4d3b-45db-acd6-47ea3b241dee">
<h2 local-id=3D"5b2f9a910737" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrinciples">=
2.2 Key Principles</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b91e5a3c2e00">The solution aligns with the <strong>AWS Well-=
Architected Framework</strong>, which consists of six pillars:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"66295b22082d" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-1.OperationalExcel=
lence">1. Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"21d8bde1-4639-48c2-9861-f1d67c7e978a">
<li local-id=3D"4b2d51fa-5c0c-49a6-ab14-0dbf5b31a116">
<p local-id=3D"57239653f4c4">Infrastructure deployed using structured AWS c=
onfigurations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8f38f46-42dc-43cc-a734-96ca78f01baa">
<p local-id=3D"18b21bb68352">Services monitored through ECS and EC2 health =
checks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"270d3e05-7c02-49c9-93ae-f750a469a070">
<p local-id=3D"e8212bd81f1f">Clear separation of application components</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"dec2b6d05d8c" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.Security">2. Sec=
urity</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"85c077ab-93ab-4c5e-a7d0-0438e98d2bd6">
<li local-id=3D"44e39949-a518-4200-b559-3b09e217c704">
<p local-id=3D"4faa5410f91f">IAM-based access control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16bc230c-ab6f-4c48-ba27-8291cfeb716d">
<p local-id=3D"1a3a869422a6">Security Groups restricting inbound traffic</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"38bb68cc-250e-414b-a54e-76a1764065e4">
<p local-id=3D"9642352ce845">Public S3 access limited via explicit bucket p=
olicies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"270c16ce-ec64-42b9-84f6-aa80ef249a11">
<p local-id=3D"2562bbce7b18">ECS tasks isolated within managed environment<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f73dee20ce48" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-3.Reliability">3. =
Reliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"de7b8bdc-2c75-42bd-a1c1-0273a4e4bd55">
<li local-id=3D"16b564c2-e429-495b-b3b0-329333265de7">
<p local-id=3D"9aa41a4241a7">ECS Service ensures desired task count is main=
tained</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"10b6df80-8b53-4dc7-8c3f-93a1b8eb34f4">
<p local-id=3D"9cb06ca7e9d5">Application Load Balancer distributes traffic<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7c907c0c-f6f6-48c9-a1b4-2bb26c725ba7">
<p local-id=3D"5e786e2b4e03">EC2 health checks validate instance availabili=
ty</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"3ccad2b463a0" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-4.PerformanceEffic=
iency">4. Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"766a20a5-a93c-44cd-b160-11edc4a65592">
<li local-id=3D"67ca7465-ae4f-4af3-badf-987e98fa889a">
<p local-id=3D"f89d71a6c2bd">Use of Fargate for serverless container scalin=
g</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a19fd227-5c07-4b00-acd5-889fb8fa5262">
<p local-id=3D"ae4bc4ca5a64">Lightweight t3.micro instance for EC2 hosting<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a9891ea8-8b4f-40b9-aa96-4a5458c5a849">
<p local-id=3D"1cd5236bd93d">Managed S3 static hosting for low-latency cont=
ent delivery</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"51e632d1c5db" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-5.CostOptimization=
">5. Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0ee5618f-d3b9-4ad8-b180-84ed56c0ecaf">
<li local-id=3D"7d8aab73-b6b5-4dcf-9fc3-3f30f269037f">
<p local-id=3D"bf26959e7568">Use of Fargate (no idle server cost)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00063ca2-0be2-42d6-baa6-ea189f2565bd">
<p local-id=3D"b9a2b9ed6e16">Right-sized EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2dfdd65-c801-4332-9b38-8f7235800868">
<p local-id=3D"71f5cc8ded42">Static hosting via S3 instead of full server c=
ompute</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d3ce953681f0" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-6.Sustainability">=
6. Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"28f44ffc-0e16-4268-bc94-b1b1bdbfccda">
<li local-id=3D"ce99a5de-4e93-471a-9c4e-ca30d62b8603">
<p local-id=3D"0f976683b604">Serverless container compute reduces unused re=
source consumption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7888f024-dc54-4a06-92d7-6c7f4c955b64">
<p local-id=3D"1e5b7bd4ad89">Optimized instance selection to avoid over-pro=
visioning</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"513d1cd7-7b67-455d-9836-da4d58f46e2a">
<h2 local-id=3D"d36d0343da5e" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"de4d20d6df02">The primary objectives of this DevOps implemen=
tation were:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9a7097b3-f5d4-4e94-931e-7178df2de420">
<li local-id=3D"2b5c86ae-5aed-40c6-b60c-394078bfd8ff">
<p local-id=3D"431536b594b1">Deploy multiple frontend applications using di=
fferent AWS services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a6b33c1-5b35-40e1-8703-2c691df67de4">
<p local-id=3D"e383ab2f55ca">Implement container-based deployment using ECS=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fea51077-6c17-4972-838e-ffc88249b555">
<p local-id=3D"a50bc7f24ba3">Host static websites via S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b30174b-548b-4567-8a37-88c986509ceb">
<p local-id=3D"60b2c99bf3fb">Deploy traditional server-based hosting using =
EC2 + Nginx</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8de63bd-c313-472d-8411-f5555c62b12b">
<p local-id=3D"bf102ba04a3e">Implement load balancing for scalable access</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f86938da-4c08-436e-a75c-946c237894e5">
<p local-id=3D"9dd3a85eaf08">Validate accessibility via public endpoints</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"1611786f-2b11-4eab-b270-7eed8ccdc640">
<p local-id=3D"0ee2081fabec">Maintain cost-effective architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a18f3489-773b-4ad3-ac20-76843d240ad3">
<h2 local-id=3D"9b1736e5d624" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"df69676c809a" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">Const=
raints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3716dbe7-fa8e-44dc-8839-2731c29625de">
<li local-id=3D"ab7fbc1a-8117-454d-adbf-b68ce8c1b145">
<p local-id=3D"a5380900c917">Limited budget (use of free-tier eligible serv=
ices where possible)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4bfa52b7-f66d-45ae-b6c9-3f87ce7fdca9">
<p local-id=3D"13e51eb3f222">Limited project duration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c859dd0-e255-4baa-b84f-796252464f83">
<p local-id=3D"f87ae1ca653c">Single-region deployment (ap-south-1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"615bcacc-69ff-4179-84c1-25f5b3bc87d1">
<p local-id=3D"736dc278103e">No automated CI/CD pipeline integration</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"1b4324c0ed0d" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">Assum=
ptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"27f78811-9375-42fe-af91-4e2063f0f0d9">
<li local-id=3D"a8cf3a43-e30e-4182-abd0-dfa6250e6db6">
<p local-id=3D"c491035d8cae">Applications are frontend-only and do not requ=
ire persistent backend storage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"91925a97-ba5c-4829-b33b-4484ebe50cde">
<p local-id=3D"7aa79b0bfd67">Traffic volume is moderate and suitable for si=
ngle-region hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c15fca0-17e8-4a0f-90cd-5b8b211cf617">
<p local-id=3D"62d6d0675406">Users access services over HTTP (SSL not confi=
gured in this phase)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f57b314a-5949-4d02-a869-d8fe6966abe6">
<p local-id=3D"700b445d9168">Basic monitoring via AWS console is sufficient=
 for this implementation</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"a927e909f66f" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5e56482af8b1"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-5-2026-12_47=
_06-AM-20260304-192002.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"23dbe7cbc=
946a66f948731722709fd3963e9178f6672677298b1b362c1911473" data-image-src=3D"=
