<p local-id=3D"97e199b7ba0a"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"bb6f8b64-609a-42cd-9869-2fd7fcbb0012">
<h2 local-id=3D"91bec82cfcd8" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ce193c29c1d3">The infrastructure is designed using AWS manag=
ed services to support multiple frontend deployment strategies. The archite=
cture includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd4d8b6b-9862-4398-bf64-828b3316e078">
<li local-id=3D"d3a7156d-4ad4-45b1-a5e9-3291024a6609">
<p local-id=3D"7d1ca2d79443">Static hosting using Amazon S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0202b2ed-e418-4a02-8090-a0ec3f39f62f">
<p local-id=3D"c682a236e925">Containerized deployments using Amazon ECS (Fa=
rgate)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af8ce6fb-b04a-422e-8ec7-e6d03a13c631">
<p local-id=3D"9ccfdecb443e">Docker image storage via Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f0bab79-17b0-48d8-acfe-a4b22817c1c5">
<p local-id=3D"179722cd0f47">Compute-based hosting using Amazon EC2 with Ng=
inx</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0f0f848-2482-491e-bbe7-adf91e712039">
<p local-id=3D"ea5676b5f1de">Traffic distribution using Application Load Ba=
lancer (ALB)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7031828d-c7aa-4a37-8c6d-dee56c3e4e9a">
<p local-id=3D"efa55705b977">Network security via Security Groups and IAM p=
olicies</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4701f6f5abea">The solution is deployed in a single AWS regio=
n and follows a modular design where each hosting method is independently v=
alidated.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"09d179d7-345f-4d74-b399-357e3dfa76a7">
