<hr local-id=3D"412f62a1-14ba-42ff-91f5-f36645287f5d">
<h2 local-id=3D"99c822e687d7" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-EC2-BasedDeploymen=
tArchitecture">EC2-Based Deployment Architecture</h2>
<p local-id=3D"340821cbb595">The EC2 deployment model uses a traditional se=
rver-based approach:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5c640778-26de-465c-ba16-567bebc31b83">
<li local-id=3D"4ef7dc1e-46dd-42d5-b4b1-734709d75252">
<p local-id=3D"b63653b16162">Amazon EC2 instance (t3.micro)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6268e3d2-f0e2-4eac-b653-244e29808fad">
<p local-id=3D"8ed1662e4acd">Nginx web server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1411f266-0bb2-4f5f-a42f-5d2e85885d9e">
<p local-id=3D"04a763a25436">Manual file deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0002f75-1134-4950-a8c2-4b56759f2930">
<p local-id=3D"1eac8505c861">Security group configuration for HTTP/SSH</p><=
/li>
</ul>
