<p local-id=3D"f1e05baa91a3">The security model balances accessibility for =
frontend hosting with controlled infrastructure exposure.<br><br>
8. Cost Optimisation</p>
<p local-id=3D"e3d7de0aa2f9">This section outlines the cost considerations,=
 right-sizing strategy, and total cost awareness applied during the impleme=
ntation of the frontend hosting architecture across AWS services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"bf32db5b63dc">The objective was to evaluate cost efficiency =
across three deployment models:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cbf8e239-d0f9-4d97-b650-d44476b2b8f6">
<li local-id=3D"3a925845-9a74-4b71-aa43-feefcfcc7495">
<p local-id=3D"9e189829eb8c">Amazon S3 (Static Hosting)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b857786a-9abc-485e-84c8-366f38451b59">
<p local-id=3D"be5c5b185d0e">Amazon ECS (Fargate =E2=80=93 Container Hostin=
g)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca6cf8ae-c43a-47ef-94ed-0a26ed78f28e">
<p local-id=3D"557a112355d8">Amazon EC2 (Virtual Machine Hosting)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1da2c6b9-1926-4157-ac85-bb8fc6563cac">
<h2 local-id=3D"fc7cf3b19b92" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-8.1TotalCostofOwne=
rship(TCO)Considerations">8.1 Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) Considerations<=
/h2>
<p local-id=3D"1564ba7e1ad9">The cost model considered the following inputs=
:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a7343c00aa57" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-InfrastructureInpu=
tsUsedforEstimation">Infrastructure Inputs Used for Estimation</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c4c3ff4d-5d2c-4338-ba6c-766ddffc1a65">
<li local-id=3D"c6d8d68b-d2d6-4e44-984b-9dc47590dd2d">
<p local-id=3D"db41a6e24aac">Instance type selection (t3.micro for EC2)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"eb1e0713-7a50-478a-80cf-bc9e9c6e0bc0">
<p local-id=3D"a76b52a61097">Fargate CPU and memory configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef4318cf-9b9d-4354-bb2a-00687da345ed">
<p local-id=3D"a5bc65fa9cbb">Number of running ECS tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6de6c84a-9318-41d8-8844-4275cf21fbab">
<p local-id=3D"ce17aaff0af9">S3 storage usage (static frontend assets)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"11baa105-5907-47e7-9a64-a441b742bb36">
<p local-id=3D"767aa373cc11">Load Balancer usage hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f498c2a-fb16-41ae-9176-86a5cb48ae20">
<p local-id=3D"a719967e5d80">Data transfer (internet egress)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f8e40b4f6f3e">Each hosting model has a different cost struct=
ure:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"2b=
27ab7d-a8c0-4495-90f6-90effcf52734" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"90ba90b9-bc71-44fa-be04-60a1011563b7">
<th data-local-id=3D"928dd51e-f82d-409b-8cd5-1bc49a49dbf7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bbb35538c488">Service</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ebee312d-9182-4fce-aaa8-5ec378c1ca46" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5831b43ce578">Cost Model Type</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0999a3d0-ae36-42c8-8570-212bd770359d">
<td data-local-id=3D"29460d14-1357-41ad-aa8f-c1f8b0180e29" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"990e244f958b">S3</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e34e6b50-0fbf-4e16-bcc4-4902a847df88" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c68024941385">Storage + Data Transfer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"90dad244-830c-4ce5-88af-4452baf69459">
<td data-local-id=3D"c6d189bd-5dfa-4449-8251-a345e0ea2494" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c2c37549f930">ECS Fargate</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dfb1e4e3-822e-41ac-aaae-643067a9d32f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab9d0b1a52f0">vCPU + Memory per running task</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"58328f8e-4d30-4f1e-b3a1-a03490e66bf5">
<td data-local-id=3D"aa1ef250-6311-4800-b798-3fc1c8574849" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e350713cb042">EC2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"22ed585d-e998-4b2d-b7be-df572add6911" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8f640317f6ba">Fixed hourly compute instance</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"50f5c607-d3fa-49a8-8ddd-fa5007948802">
<td data-local-id=3D"c2f29266-e546-4131-94d7-eafbc01ae4e3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7e6c2c17e2b7">ALB</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b3b4e75e-31d7-4cb2-b2ac-0296137ff580" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b21e761d1684">Hourly + Data processed</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"cd389dfc-3050-4646-b178-2efc0be7726b">
<h2 local-id=3D"1556f61d67c8" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-8.2Right-SizingStr=
ategy">8.2 Right-Sizing Strategy</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d8035862a6c4">Cost optimisation was achieved through proper =
resource selection:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"fd3d3b296238" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-EC2Right-Sizing">E=
C2 Right-Sizing</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3a80771c-a280-4873-9e03-e3f315e762dd">
<li local-id=3D"dab13bfd-27e6-4ee5-b3c8-9fedd0dfef1d">
<p local-id=3D"90c11164a314">Used <strong>t3.micro</strong> instance (free-=
tier eligible).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9e566b2-bece-492f-9c0a-bfdc69bf145d">
<p local-id=3D"25a3529235d9">Suitable for lightweight static frontend hosti=
ng.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46169b38-c5ec-46c8-b4f1-b539a4f77654">
<p local-id=3D"82b354ce4252">Avoided over-provisioned instance types.</p></=
li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"40cf1b706229" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-ECSFargateConfigur=
ation">ECS Fargate Configuration</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a635dab4-d67c-4488-b2c1-ff98974d4c9e">
<li local-id=3D"c5839d58-ee93-468f-bee5-74a5e4cb88c0">
<p local-id=3D"ba4b18058990">Configured minimal CPU and memory allocation f=
or frontend containers.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69e7c607-8daf-40dc-a470-4c3e1cc4046b">
<p local-id=3D"175b156723b4">Maintained only required task count.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c91d6ab-83ed-4819-8f63-6fa580b722ae">
<p local-id=3D"1387e89d050a">Avoided idle EC2 cluster nodes (serverless com=
pute model).</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f0194d544df" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-S3StaticHosting">S=
3 Static Hosting</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4c6ab5dd-84ec-4890-9466-f5c88c7cd9d5">
<li local-id=3D"51f612ef-2574-40ec-bee9-23c1d9fe9fc2">
<p local-id=3D"357c1feb0122">No compute resources required.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e02f7df7-77dd-41ce-a29b-3eefd6dc7044">
<p local-id=3D"1144ea43fa50">No idle server cost.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a8a5ecc-3403-4434-8801-b9f4988559d4">
<p local-id=3D"0319f317d080">Only storage and bandwidth-based billing.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b503785167d6">This ensured infrastructure was aligned with a=
pplication workload.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7aa48b77-d1c8-4dc1-a497-51bf42dda7d2">
<h2 local-id=3D"facf30fedb83" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-8.3CostComparisonO=
verview">8.3 Cost Comparison Overview</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"446a350af489" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-AmazonS3">Amazon S=
3</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"94dc94ce-442e-427d-84af-1acbd114d9b5">
<li local-id=3D"f8f61a96-ae80-4521-9a85-3549f9365a85">
<p local-id=3D"4257e6770ed8">Lowest operational cost.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4899ee5b-8833-4fd0-b614-b5caf7a4ad43">
<p local-id=3D"49406239fd0e">No server management.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"518bda27-b22d-4123-8adc-e3365cbc232b">
<p local-id=3D"f34ca11872fa">Ideal for purely static applications.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"cf3f7056ec5c" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-AmazonECS(Fargate)=
">Amazon ECS (Fargate)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ed5215df-619a-407a-a0a0-83122b870f36">
<li local-id=3D"b3426b41-f37d-440d-8dca-3becbe5249d6">
<p local-id=3D"92b28fa7f69b">Moderate cost.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef92c146-fa47-4ee2-b755-e495dbb3d69a">
<p local-id=3D"4dd98d7588b8">Pay-per-use container compute.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c4d29105-c282-40b6-b040-f1d691315cd1">
<p local-id=3D"4ee4dd04d4b1">Scalable and production-ready.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7193af47-ba97-4bfa-9b22-44fa915c1c22">
<p local-id=3D"ff7bb199d0cd">ALB introduces additional cost component.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d4fd78f25528" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-AmazonEC2">Amazon =
EC2</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2e5a2157-f203-497b-ad7e-13a794de3769">
<li local-id=3D"b5a53a8f-f1ae-4e27-8a05-e9e320e8a087">
<p local-id=3D"e0429370b365">Fixed compute cost regardless of traffic.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"8618cd4c-8b91-487b-8fcf-4dea0d2968a9">
<p local-id=3D"670cf99eda9d">Requires manual scaling.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dd87252-8111-40a1-8f45-a0b66c1b4928">
<p local-id=3D"330d430e1b64">Higher operational overhead compared to S3.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f25c8f44-eba0-48f3-b758-0afc50895d63">
<h2 local-id=3D"71c4e4641536" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-8.4BusinessValueAn=
alysis">8.4 Business Value Analysis</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a752e6dd4e1f">The deployment comparison provides business in=
sights:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"5135e5d649cf" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-S3">S3</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2dee8c09-00fc-4981-8dbc-bd3611d7fa1e">
<li local-id=3D"9ae1f9b8-37f7-4cf5-949e-aa97e1cb9957">
<p local-id=3D"b5216c9e618d">Best suited for cost-sensitive static web host=
ing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44a74589-0077-468b-93d4-5c0189b3a4ea">
<p local-id=3D"3c0775523606">Minimal operational complexity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c87ef9b1-3e87-4543-947a-586854e2d1ce">
<p local-id=3D"1f9b57bb2e35">Ideal for marketing sites and simple frontend =
apps.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"cb72ebb2b60d" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-ECS">ECS</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ff7027f7-24ed-42bf-8ab5-deb4b4fa5272">
<li local-id=3D"0087d454-f71c-42c3-bc63-c49d02712999">
<p local-id=3D"436ad08008c8">Suitable for scalable, evolving applications.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9dd8d909-57e0-4321-a09f-f3ef3bdbe1c4">
<p local-id=3D"21e775d09925">Supports container standardization.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dc2f9c3-899f-42dc-b96f-94168c25f05f">
<p local-id=3D"77ee66d9a007">Enables easier CI/CD integration in future.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6631cf06df8c" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-EC2">EC2</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"aba04bcd-c93a-4d10-a7b9-7faf3cc285f3">
<li local-id=3D"dcafb7b2-072a-47ed-ba76-55fb4862e85e">
<p local-id=3D"e989527d1155">Offers full control over server configuration.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad0ca386-5df4-4dc3-999e-3234d9a1a742">
<p local-id=3D"a821c5944e6a">Suitable for custom server-level requirements.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"642c6ae0-6731-4e05-be7e-1ac57efb36ea">
<p local-id=3D"6f1d6189c30a">Higher maintenance responsibility.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"890f6f2e-439c-4739-a8ab-59b40199a9d4">
<h2 local-id=3D"efbfaab8fdd6" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-8.5CostEfficiencyS=
ummary">8.5 Cost Efficiency Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2c5e5e7a917c">The implementation demonstrates:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"391be2bf-40a9-4a5f-8cfd-472a72bd6368">
<li local-id=3D"b753d4b0-70aa-43d8-b854-425d4e4f61a2">
<p local-id=3D"e66660c85f14">Efficient resource selection.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"abcf8bfc-686e-40f0-8b23-ca95ae6f1ef5">
<p local-id=3D"6b249577f4a6">Avoidance of unnecessary compute allocation.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2560e7e-c585-4203-8cae-536703115f88">
<p local-id=3D"8e9ac4295db8">Alignment of infrastructure type with applicat=
ion complexity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2ce8601b-f9f0-4f77-89c2-4426f602b26a">
<p local-id=3D"d6e1259f4bd1">Evaluation of cost-performance trade-offs.</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"47649b362d5a">The comparative cost modelling supports data-d=
riven decision-making for selecting a standardized frontend hosting model.<=
/p>
<h1 local-id=3D"fc9be87c35fe" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-9.ImplementationTi=
meline">9. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<p local-id=3D"67f3b0dc538a">This section outlines the phased implementatio=
n approach followed during the deployment of frontend applications across A=
WS services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9a480c7980d7">Although the overall execution was completed w=
ithin a limited timeframe, the work was structured into logical stages to e=
nsure validation and stability.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c55a86c8-00f9-40f5-90e3-74b92201adae">
<h2 local-id=3D"1a1e70fd653a" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-9.1MilestonesandDe=
liverables">9.1 Milestones and Deliverables</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"91376cdea5e8" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-Phase1:Environment=
SetupandStaticHosting(S3)">Phase 1: Environment Setup and Static Hosting (S=
3)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8f816bfa-a2f4-4f77-bf63-da4fd5f35ea8">
<li local-id=3D"53fd4ea6-240c-4f07-819e-ce04d17600bc">
<p local-id=3D"0b16ffe06be0">Creation of S3 buckets for each application</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"3155b580-fa54-4d6d-8ab8-fb7508b4ec06">
<p local-id=3D"80efed4876ec">Static website hosting configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"456e229b-8ae0-4e1a-a8ea-3ada6e469e5a">
<p local-id=3D"5b74778c5296">Bucket policy configuration for public read ac=
cess</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"241b3a07-7dea-4c27-90ea-ad489cb134bc">
<p local-id=3D"d9f5dff578ae">Upload of frontend files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3954ea6-f3a8-4497-9720-ecf7aae317bf">
<p local-id=3D"5a2eb05ebb07">Public endpoint validation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"42a0b3c3e798"><strong>Deliverable:</strong><br>
Three frontend applications successfully accessible via S3 website endpoint=
s.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"763c62fd-3724-4af0-ae8c-7c622d9261a3">
<h3 local-id=3D"a55106327176" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-Phase2:Containeriz=
ationandECSDeployment">Phase 2: Containerization and ECS Deployment</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ddf9616f-44f8-426d-8069-f542b06e323d">
<li local-id=3D"513f0be6-ea73-4350-b37c-78188884ba00">
<p local-id=3D"bc1b7cc51dda">Dockerfile creation for frontend applications<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d87630b-0b14-4e19-b2de-e40f3816166a">
<p local-id=3D"f1f0c791896b">Local Docker image build</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2af373dd-6ed6-4b22-9b62-ac952bd5926a">
<p local-id=3D"8e0e35eb6379">Image push to Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a818414-fea2-42a4-9d80-1ad29e574457">
<p local-id=3D"53ccadd2101c">ECS cluster creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38f0260c-56f9-4e47-a8ed-d3a1e9c3fe4e">
<p local-id=3D"7486ea7d9060">Task definition configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"532ab8e9-984e-4ca0-8aa5-dfd9a7502efb">
<p local-id=3D"b0b1d40968b5">ECS service setup with Fargate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"60de6052-8618-4855-94f7-fa5f6042b4fe">
<p local-id=3D"82879c8d14da">Application Load Balancer configuration</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"7f0b3c85-b379-40bf-855b-5b954f2afc92">
<p local-id=3D"59e04c18fa61">Public DNS validation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f1d91b193ee4"><strong>Deliverable:</strong><br>
Containerized applications deployed and accessible via ALB DNS endpoint.</p=
>
<hr local-id=3D"4c1e8a7d-ddef-4ae9-95f3-82afca17e59e">
<h3 local-id=3D"e43990f21849" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-Phase3:EC2-BasedDe=
ployment">Phase 3: EC2-Based Deployment</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"6104af92-4877-4b88-87c0-71b70b558128">
<li local-id=3D"ed77918f-9b12-4106-90bf-927c284f9a95">
<p local-id=3D"6ef453553e50">EC2 instance provisioning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce3d1ec1-fee1-414b-9cab-6390ed3fee7e">
<p local-id=3D"a1dea2f74ce3">Security group configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48eca8b3-a220-49e9-893a-0b0e90e29a4a">
<p local-id=3D"287aeaa17bb5">Nginx installation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"097d5a1b-4588-4c50-b50f-eb985a3fec27">
<p local-id=3D"bc0a41040a37">Removal of default server content</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe199478-d62f-4db0-b534-d47e535a0cc0">
<p local-id=3D"c36215615c5f">Deployment of frontend files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dbe6df68-20e0-4bb7-842c-dc59bfae8565">
<p local-id=3D"c02602c030c6">Service validation via public IP</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"114b31011894"><strong>Deliverable:</strong><br>
Frontend applications hosted on EC2 and accessible via public IP.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b5efbd06-16d7-4564-8b0a-22502b545880">
