<hr local-id=3D"a916a7f9-8116-4f47-a251-4b0d094ea147">
<h1 local-id=3D"8088a4f447cc" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-10.ContinuousImpro=
vement">10. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<p local-id=3D"fce0617f956a">Although this implementation focused on deploy=
ment validation, future improvements can enhance automation, scalability, a=
nd security.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ea7a3bc7-1fbc-4da6-ba50-3af3b2730248">
<h2 local-id=3D"d905f3b85664" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-10.1FeedbackandRet=
rospectives">10.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7303db2ee4e5">Key observations from the implementation:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0deb6030-526b-46a1-986e-d81bc8b5fe8a">
<li local-id=3D"b3f0cf9b-567f-4e0b-9b93-ff88f70937dd">
<p local-id=3D"af36f4bf59f7">S3 provides the simplest and most cost-effecti=
ve frontend hosting.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5373b892-5360-4722-9b7c-c13c0552a8ba">
<p local-id=3D"3113ce1e3980">ECS offers better scalability but introduces c=
onfiguration complexity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36be579a-dbb9-4d25-8918-be6229010a44">
<p local-id=3D"ece72f3c58db">EC2 requires manual management and has higher =
operational overhead.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8f03def08328">Lessons learned:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"eed5406b-f0e4-41fc-ba21-64b5339fc0e1">
<li local-id=3D"246aaa0a-2a5f-447d-814e-7c487d949280">
<p local-id=3D"6f8e73a760cc">Containerized deployments improve portability.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73ccd5a9-d6f5-4a46-8282-4478a0dcb2ab">
<p local-id=3D"3d67d0423059">Managed services reduce infrastructure managem=
ent burden.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e06857cf-41fe-42b9-860c-0ef298aa5939">
<p local-id=3D"7c357569b585">Proper security configuration is critical for =
public-facing services.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cf3addbf-d8dd-4edd-a0f5-e0b92197f0ae">
<h2 local-id=3D"6fd466957af8" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-10.2IterativeEnhan=
cements">10.2 Iterative Enhancements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e2cd5d6b0cbb">The following improvements can be implemented =
in future iterations:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"411047a9-6ee6-42d2-9889-cebe4748734e">
<li local-id=3D"39393974-1264-4a5d-9c87-683db3c9cb84">
<p local-id=3D"31f6a2368647">Integration of CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions =
or AWS CodePipeline)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83ec4873-7eac-492a-8659-93714ad7e369">
<p local-id=3D"3c9aa6918983">SSL/TLS implementation using AWS Certificate M=
anager</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2c247e4-38c5-4268-9716-51e8af4bf322">
<p local-id=3D"84ac28defa92">CloudWatch monitoring and alert configuration<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"548b009f-0231-4772-b443-5d1e3dcfe2c5">
<p local-id=3D"a3d154393956">Infrastructure as Code using Terraform or AWS =
CloudFormation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f8505c01-4567-49e1-b205-3de1d963b859">
<p local-id=3D"7e715582aab4">Multi-AZ high availability setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb67d934-e3e5-4241-9b62-e12ab6e37db0">
<p local-id=3D"dff649d71b5c">CDN integration using Amazon CloudFront for im=
proved performance</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e61e76caab24">These enhancements would transition the soluti=
on from validation-level implementation to production-grade architecture.</=
p>
<hr local-id=3D"48d38e46-3361-4fe3-b914-290bbf9adbd1">
<h1 local-id=3D"518119801d1c" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-11.Conclusion">11.=
 Conclusion</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"f9cb86cc-6a4f-49c1-ba08-a12fc0ba4be7">
<h2 local-id=3D"baa29219d73f" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-11.1Summary">11.1 =
Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d6fa61c38580">This document presented a comprehensive DevOps=
 implementation for deploying frontend applications using three AWS hosting=
 models:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ae7f7e5c-efca-4951-a994-09060dbb25a5">
<li local-id=3D"513f1fe1-a62e-4244-9f14-48d4398ad8ec">
<p local-id=3D"1339c33a1f93">Static Hosting via Amazon S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1cbdee7f-1cbd-4669-8c43-d4d4fb5c2687">
<p local-id=3D"dea734fab970">Containerized Deployment via Amazon ECS (Farga=
te)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89e3ddf0-6f31-48fc-bce5-5cc9ccbd7993">
<p local-id=3D"6566ae850061">Virtual Machine Hosting via Amazon EC2 with Ng=
inx</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"68fc770eaba4">Each deployment model was implemented, validat=
ed, and evaluated based on cost, scalability, operational complexity, and a=
rchitectural suitability.</p>
<p local-id=3D"430375e142cc">The implementation demonstrates:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c550b134-3baf-408f-96cf-a734f2c5a5db">
<li local-id=3D"1687ef98-303d-4d6f-aa0c-730e010a5e6e">
<p local-id=3D"1f69eb2aaec5">Cloud-native deployment capability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa4335c6-115d-4f65-81df-20a30e50f227">
<p local-id=3D"73f584758e9e">Container orchestration knowledge</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94606b09-4cbc-4588-b454-70708520c491">
<p local-id=3D"8a5cb813f284">Infrastructure configuration and validation</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"94c25518-8ec8-4ccd-81cc-7ad39baa375b">
<p local-id=3D"e08626888d24">Cost-aware architecture design</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2fc6d718-2b02-4d8d-ab4e-fa4252da8cab">
<p local-id=3D"9629db3e4d77">Security-conscious configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6c40a76b-adbb-4dfc-9fdf-e85f029c5fe0">
<h2 local-id=3D"ab280fc4b182" id=3D"T4-TechnicalDocument-11.2NextSteps">11.=
2 Next Steps</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d335e6639979">Based on the evaluation:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b9352bad-0fbb-4b37-9c24-94b80ecb9af9">
<li local-id=3D"3dc35699-449a-4574-90f0-c28426b51a6a">
<p local-id=3D"0691b684bd3f">Select a standardized frontend hosting model a=
ligned with business requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a049657-2e67-4100-9bf3-fd01dc77dfdd">
<p local-id=3D"934d6583e16d">Integrate CI/CD automation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d38a6ff-bf69-45d2-8eb7-32ee9f2d2c7d">
<p local-id=3D"fb704ad22dac">Implement HTTPS and advanced monitoring</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"62f97cc8-0574-4575-86be-672b3f6a2d5d">
<p local-id=3D"9aa055ac3c64">Transition to Infrastructure as Code</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed6108c4-0626-4ea0-b1a9-182d95188e02">
<p local-id=3D"ff7bc9775d31">Optimize deployment pipelines for scalability<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b5f33e1cc3a8">This solution provides a strong foundation for=
 future cloud-native frontend deployments.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
